SEARCH
Package com.software.fitness_system

Class LoadAndSaveEntities

java.lang.Object
com.software.fitness_system.LoadAndSaveEntities
public class LoadAndSaveEntities extends Object
Utility class for handling the loading and saving of various entities in the Fitness Management System. This class provides methods to read data from persistent storage and save updated data back to files.
Author:
Muath Hassoun, Alaa Alawneh, Ammar Shafii

      public static boolean saveCustomSubscriptionPlanToFile(Map<String,CustomPlan> CustomSubscriptionPlanMap, String CustomSubscriptionPlanFile)
      Saves the custom subscription plan map to a file. If the file doesn't exist, a new file will be created.
      Parameters:
      CustomSubscriptionPlanMap - the map of custom subscription plans to save
      CustomSubscriptionPlanFile - the path to the file where the data will be saved
      Returns:
      true if the data was saved successfully, false otherwise
